{"tid":957291,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"（怒屌蝗婦)打唔到尖仲想排頭位？冇病下嘛！","createTime":"2018-12-27T02:15:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T06:52:42.000Z","uid":5960,"like":96,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"35f2da68f888a1a9c7b941a8fb7c20be3eec6a2a","tid":957291,"uid":5960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:15:17.000Z","msg":"是咁的，<br />\n今日小弟如常返工 (係窮呀DLGH<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，<br />\n係月台排隊上地鐵嘅時候，眼見前面個車箱都冇曬位，咁我同旁邊嘅西裝大叔都好自然咁，企係黃線後面等下一架車啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jaekPyt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjaekPyt.png&h=aba68c67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係關門前三秒，有個三十幾歲嘅女人見車門未關，衝過去車門前面想逼入架車。車入面根本冇曬位，個女人夾硬用手推人，想撞入去，但腳都踏唔入車箱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fTBvskG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfTBvskG.png&h=bfd07e77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n突然，個女人踏唔入車箱，竟然詐詐弟想退後兩步，借d椅撞我向後，打尖霸頭位！<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，打唔到尖仲想排頭位？冇病下嘛！<br />\n<br />\n好彩小弟身型都唔細份，紮行個馬，蹻埋雙手，等個蝗婦一撞埋黎，就用手勁震開佢。<br />\n如圖：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BAeXRRA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBAeXRRA.png&h=9e111d3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我怒屌：喂！企返去後面啦！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女人(帶鄉音)：哎呀好多人上唔到車......<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我：企返去後面啦！一早知上唔到車仲插上黎！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女人(仲想退後)：哎呀上唔到車......<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我：企返去後面呀！打尖上唔到車仲想排頭位？冇病下嘛！<br />\n<br />\n最後個蝗婦死死地氣，口upup咁行左去第二條隊嘅隊尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌，香港人唔好再同啲蝗蟲講禮儀啦，啲蝗蟲最叻就係扮曬野，著數攞到盡，真係唔屌唔屌得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e094951158e8a98579536f8b399c2c2a5234521","tid":957291,"uid":150899,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35f2da68f888a1a9c7b941a8fb7c20be3eec6a2a","tid":957291,"uid":5960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:15:17.000Z","msg":"是咁的，<br />\n今日小弟如常返工 (係窮呀DLGH<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，<br />\n係月台排隊上地鐵嘅時候，眼見前面個車箱都冇曬位，咁我同旁邊嘅西裝大叔都好自然咁，企係黃線後面等下一架車啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jaekPyt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjaekPyt.png&h=aba68c67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n係關門前三秒，有個三十幾歲嘅女人見車門未關，衝過去車門前面想逼入架車。車入面根本冇曬位，個女人夾硬用手推人，想撞入去，但腳都踏唔入車箱。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fTBvskG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfTBvskG.png&h=bfd07e77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n突然，個女人踏唔入車箱，竟然詐詐弟想退後兩步，借d椅撞我向後，打尖霸頭位！<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母，打唔到尖仲想排頭位？冇病下嘛！<br />\n<br />\n好彩小弟身型都唔細份，紮行個馬，蹻埋雙手，等個蝗婦一撞埋黎，就用手勁震開佢。<br />\n如圖：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BAeXRRA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBAeXRRA.png&h=9e111d3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" c