aces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我：企返去後面呀！打尖上唔到車仲想排頭位？冇病下嘛！<br />\n<br />\n最後個蝗婦死死地氣，口upup咁行左去第二條隊嘅隊尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌，香港人唔好再同啲蝗蟲講禮儀啦，啲蝗蟲最叻就係扮曬野，著數攞到盡，真係唔屌唔屌得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:38:47.000Z","msg":"係大陸個邊啲地鐵返工時間好爆架，所以佢地係慣左夾硬迫入去。<br />\n不過落到黎香港就唔好咁啦...<br />\n之前我去上海日日比班仆街迫住，仲要勁大動作，日日係個車廂到好似打架咁..."},{"pid":"fafad5817f0393880f1672a8801f540aaf28dafd","tid":957291,"uid":28546,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"699b8ae39a91044572dbdfc6133b3b8b4e47e4b3","tid":957291,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"f25180d7b321204e95d79792b230215d08cbc1c7","tid":957291,"uid":28546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e24abf2bd0857e75bc50285541281e095f695ca","tid":957291,"uid":213877,"like":1,"dislike":34,"score":-33,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:24:29.000Z","msg":"又劃圖又講解搞咁撚多野放上網都唔敢現實屌鳩佢開佢波<br />\n<br />\n連登仔真係好可悲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:28:36.000Z","msg":"你打唔成尖都唔敢現實屌鳩樓主開佢波<br />\n<br />\n蝗種人真係好可悲"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:30:33.000Z","msg":"係呀，我屌撚埋你老母<br />\n你老母就高潮啦<br />\n戇鳩仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 智障上連登 發爛炸又淨係識講粗口"},{"pid":"098f0b37f49e112aedcb5ede73e5a0264449b6d6","tid":957291,"uid":54871,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T02:47:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4637e17e4d48befbabe456ec918ea120357d71f","tid":957291,"uid":137